= Andreas Hermes

Hermes is an agriculture scientist who seeks to represent the interests of small and medium-sized peasants in the party. [? if green_front = 1: He is also an important figure in the <span style="color: #0dba1e;">**Green Front**</span> through his leadership of the <span style="color: #000000;">**VdB**</span>. ?]




